- **Twitter API**: Get at https://developer.twitter.com

To use APIs:
1. Get API key from provider
2. Create `.env` file in project root:
   ```
   HIBP_API_KEY=your_key_here
   GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_key_here
   TWITTER_API_KEY=your_key_here
   ```

